Esselte Business Systems Inc'sEsselte Meto division said it has acquired the Antonson AmericaCo, a subsidiary of &lt;Antonson Machines AB>, of Sweden.    Esselte said the Antonson unit, based in LaPorte, Indiana,manufactures scales and label printers. The company said thepurchase is part of a plan to increase the range of retailelectronic scales being offered by Esselte in the U.S.    It said the acquisition will enble Esselte to increase itsdistribution base in its effort to grow in the U.S. Reuter&#3;